    "title": "Option to use dark theme for Windows",
    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nAn option in settings to switch between light and dark theme. Will be great if it works on every OS like Electrum. However, created the issue specifically for 'Windows' because https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gui/issues/68#issuecomment-873549059\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13405205/124391068-63e17c80-dd0c-11eb-818c-d867e89df603.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13405205/124391893-68a82f80-dd10-11eb-9d1f-098979387114.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\n1. Workarounds for Linux: https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gui/issues/68#issuecomment-678196654\r\n2. Not use GUI\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nI tried few things: https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gui/issues/68#issuecomment-794431238. Worked partially for Linux but didn't work on Windows. \r\n\r\nAlso tried running master branch on Windows but there is no change in GUI.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13405205/124391958-c50b4f00-dd10-11eb-87b5-e571602ca372.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13405205/124391966-d05e7a80-dd10-11eb-90fc-a2c6b2f52605.png)\r\n\r\n",
